data.description: Impressive 2-story foyer, 9ft. ceilings on both levels. 4 beds, 3.5 baths on a tranquil cul-de-sac. Circular layout seamlessly connects living/dining areas, complemented by a cozy home office. Kitchen designed for foodies: gas cooktop island, double wall ovens, double sinks, dishwasher, pantry, and reverse osmosis water. Step-down family room with gas fireplace opens to deck and patio. Luxurious primary bed boasts ensuite with soaking tub, walk-in shower, water closet, and spacious walk-in closet. 2 beds, guest bath, 19x19 bonus room, and laundry chute complete 2nd level. New carpet, luxury vinyl flooring in basement, updated windows, roof, siding in 2023. Finished basement with rec room, second primary bed, walk-in shower, and Egress window. Energy-efficient furnace with humidifier (2020). Well-maintained exterior, 3-car garage. The 19x19 bonus room could be a fifth bedroom. Experience comfort, style, located near shopping, WPAFB, WSU and I-70.
